Zapping a '''wand of invisibility''' causes the target to temporarily become [[invisible]]. It is essentially identical to the [[Invisibility]] spell, and if used on the player, causes 1-2 points of immediate [[magic contamination]] followed by slow accumulation for the duration of the effect. [[Wand]]s of invisibility are slightly inferior to [[potions of invisibility]], as these inflict no initial contamination. They are very uncommon. A wand of invisibility can hold at most 9 charges.

==History==
Wands of invisibility were removed in [[0.18]].
